partnerDetails.about: CQ Electrical cc has successfully been trading as an electrical supplier for the past 15 years. Our vision is not only to be the best electrical retailer in the East of Pretoria, but also to grow into a competitive wholesaler in the electrical industry over time. The close corporation was established in the year 2000 and started trading as an electrical supplier in 2002.
